{"tid":1704174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警告]ROAD BLOCK 唔好加埋炸彈","createTime":"2019-11-10T14:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T02:21:28.000Z","uid":250979,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6dee08280374fd7d3d3bf7ce6a4abae99eca8fcf","tid":1704174,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"我好怕D 暴徙想突破運動樽頸<br />\n等D 阿SIR 折ROAD BLOCK 果陣被炸斷手腳<br />\n之前見過個POST 咩哥士的+通渠水+黃粉會爆炸既NEWS<br />\n好擔心暴徙照辦煮碗, 分分鐘連水炮車都無埋<br />\n希望和理非既示威者, 勸住D 暴徙收手<br />\n如果和理非屋企有需要買哥士的, 通渠水或者黃粉呢類野<br />\n買完見到警察, 以免阿SIR 難做, 擺響路邊算喇, 有機會先拎返啦<br />\n呢D 時勢, 大家收手啦, 唔好升級喇"},{"pid":"861172aebe33d993c2f6bd8bbe1ceac47c3a6ec1","tid":1704174,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"我都好怕 紙盒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/HKIP2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKIP2&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=faa9feac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/HKIP2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ws9KMEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fws9KMEO.jpg&h=ae373530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Hong Kong Independence Party <br />\n5 agendas </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n(1)  UK has the mandate from the People of Hong Kong to annul the Sino-British Joint Declaration right away; Also should the US subsequently abolish the HK Policy Act.<br />\n<br />\n(2) the UK and the US governments are requested by the Hongkongers for taking on the PRC&rsquo;s illegal occupation of Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n(3)  We require the United Kingdom to enforce those three unterminated treaties over Hong Kong sovereignty ( the Treaty of Nanking; the Convention of Peking; the Second Convention of Peking ).<br />\n<br />\n(4) We demand Anglo-American or Nato joint military base in Hong Kong on a permanent basis, the expense of which will be covered by ourselves!